title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Port of Houston
description:
In this video we will have a look at the free addon which has been released for the Port of Houston for MSFS 2020. The addon adds cargo terminals but also several factories which are close to the terminal to MSFS, 

If you would like to try the scenery yourself, download it via the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/31638/houston-cargo-terminal-houston-tx-usa
